data.description: Must See Inside This Magnificent Home! As You Enter Into the Open Foyer You'll Be Amazed. Step Down Into the Spacious Sunken Living Room, Entertain in the Formal Dining Room or Relax in the Family Room w/Gas Fireplace and New Frieze Carpeting, Updated Kitchen with 42-inch Cabinets. 4 Large Bedrooms on the Main Floor (One is Currently Used as an Office But Can Easily Be Converted Back). Wait Until You See the Amazing Finished Lower Level With a Game Room, 2nd Family Room, 5th Bedroom, Walk-in Cedar Closet & Full Bath, This Added Space Makes This Home Over 2600 Square Feet. And There is Still More in the Beautifully Landscaped Fenced Yard with Inground Pool and One of the Largest Lots in the Subdivision. Just Imagine a Warm Summer Day Relaxing in Your Own Private Paradise
